00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:58,990
And [INAUDIBLE] can
 not kill himself.

404
00:30:58,990 --> 00:31:01,070
You understand?

405
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:03,020
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

406
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:06,170
Only silver
 kills the wolf man.

407
00:31:06,170 --> 00:31:09,080
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

408
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:14,460
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

409
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:18,210
You ever shot?

410
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:19,030
No.

