00:42:00,270 --> 00:42:04,200
[SOBS]

531
00:42:12,570 --> 00:42:15,050
Oh, my god.
 Oh.

532
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:26,680
Uncle Peter?

533
00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:37,320
This was my destiny, to be
 a thing of wonder and terror

534
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,790
and then to die.

535
00:42:42,220 --> 00:42:43,200
Do not cry.

536
00:42:46,160 --> 00:42:47,430
Do not be sad for me.

537
00:43:08,750 --> 00:43:10,960
I talked to your mother.

538
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:12,710
You will be met in Geneva.

539
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:23,490
[SIGHS] The train should
 be here any minute.

